#. <section class="sutta" id="an5.23"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an5.23:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 5"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an5.23:0.2"
msgid "3. Pañcaṅgikavagga"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an5.23:0.3"
msgid "23. Upakkilesasutta"
msgstr ""

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an5.23:1.1"
msgid ""
"“Pañcime, bhikkhave, jātarūpassa upakkilesā, yehi upakkilesehi upakkiliṭṭhaṃ "
"jātarūpaṃ na ceva mudu hoti na ca kammaniyaṃ na ca pabhassaraṃ pabhaṅgu ca "
"na ca sammā upeti kammāya."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an5.23:1.2"
msgid "Katame pañca?"
msgstr ""

#. VAR: sajjhaṃ → sajjhu (bj)
msgctxt "an5.23:1.3"
msgid "Ayo, lohaṃ, tipu, sīsaṃ, sajjhaṃ—"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an5.23:1.4"
msgid ""
"ime kho, bhikkhave, pañca jātarūpassa upakkilesā, yehi upakkilesehi "
"upakkiliṭṭhaṃ jātarūpaṃ na ceva mudu hoti na ca kammaniyaṃ na ca pabhassaraṃ "
"pabhaṅgu ca na ca sammā upeti kammāya."
msgstr ""

#. VAR: vimuttaṃ → vippamuttaṃ (bj)
msgctxt "an5.23:1.5"
msgid ""
"Yato ca kho, bhikkhave, jātarūpaṃ imehi pañcahi upakkilesehi vimuttaṃ hoti, "
"taṃ hoti jātarūpaṃ mudu ca kammaniyañca pabhassarañca na ca pabhaṅgu sammā "
"upeti kammāya."
msgstr ""

#. VAR: Yassā yassā ca → yassa kassaci (s1-3, pts1)
msgctxt "an5.23:1.6"
msgid ""
"Yassā yassā ca piḷandhanavikatiyā ākaṅkhati—yadi muddikāya yadi kuṇḍalāya "
"yadi gīveyyakāya yadi suvaṇṇamālāya—tañcassa atthaṃ anubhoti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli3.17"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an5.23:2.1"
msgid ""
"Evamevaṃ kho, bhikkhave, pañcime cittassa upakkilesā, yehi upakkilesehi "
"upakkiliṭṭhaṃ cittaṃ na ceva mudu hoti na ca kammaniyaṃ na ca pabhassaraṃ "
"pabhaṅgu ca na ca sammā samādhiyati āsavānaṃ khayāya."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an5.23:2.2"
msgid "Katame pañca?"
msgstr ""

#. VAR: thinamiddhaṃ → thīnamiddhaṃ (bj, s1-3, km, pts1)
msgctxt "an5.23:2.3"
msgid "Kāmacchando, byāpādo, thinamiddhaṃ, uddhaccakukkuccaṃ, vicikicchā—"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an5.23:2.4"
msgid ""
"ime kho, bhikkhave, pañca cittassa upakkilesā yehi upakkilesehi "
"upakkiliṭṭhaṃ cittaṃ na ceva mudu hoti na ca kammaniyaṃ na ca pabhassaraṃ "
"pabhaṅgu ca na ca sammā samādhiyati āsavānaṃ khayāya."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an5.23:2.5"
msgid ""
"Yato ca kho, bhikkhave, cittaṃ imehi pañcahi upakkilesehi vimuttaṃ hoti, taṃ "
"hoti cittaṃ mudu ca kammaniyañca pabhassarañca na ca pabhaṅgu sammā "
"samādhiyati āsavānaṃ khayāya."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an5.23:2.6"
msgid ""
"Yassa yassa ca abhiññāsacchikaraṇīyassa dhammassa cittaṃ abhininnāmeti "
"abhiññāsacchikiriyāya tatra tatreva sakkhibhabbataṃ pāpuṇāti sati sati "
"āyatane."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
#. VAR: candimasūriye → candimasuriye (bj, s1-3, km, pts1)
#. VAR: parimaseyyaṃ → parāmaseyyaṃ (s1-3, pts1, mr)
msgctxt "an5.23:3.1"
msgid ""
"So sace ākaṅkhati: ‘anekavihitaṃ iddhividhaṃ paccanubhaveyyaṃ—ekopi hutvā "
"bahudhā assaṃ, bahudhāpi hutvā eko assaṃ; āvibhāvaṃ, tirobhāvaṃ; tirokuṭṭaṃ "
"tiropākāraṃ tiropabbataṃ asajjamāno gaccheyyaṃ, seyyathāpi ākāse; "
"pathaviyāpi ummujjanimujjaṃ kareyyaṃ, seyyathāpi udake; udakepi abhijjamāno "
"gaccheyyaṃ, seyyathāpi pathaviyaṃ; ākāsepi pallaṅkena kameyyaṃ, seyyathāpi "
"pakkhī sakuṇo; imepi candimasūriye evaṃmahiddhike evaṃmahānubhāve pāṇinā "
"parimaseyyaṃ parimajjeyyaṃ yāva brahmalokāpi kāyena vasaṃ vatteyyan’ti, "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an5.23:3.2"
msgid "tatra tatreva sakkhibhabbataṃ pāpuṇāti sati sati āyatane."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "an5.23:4.1"
msgid ""
"So sace ākaṅkhati: ‘dibbāya sotadhātuyā visuddhāya atikkantamānusikāya ubho "
"sadde suṇeyyaṃ—dibbe ca mānuse ca ye dūre santike cā’ti, "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an5.23:4.2"
msgid "tatra tatreva sakkhibhabbataṃ pāpuṇāti sati sati āyatane."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli3.18"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "an5.23:5.1"
msgid ""
"So sace ākaṅkhati: ‘parasattānaṃ parapuggalānaṃ cetasā ceto paricca "
"pajāneyyaṃ—"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an5.23:5.2"
msgid ""
"sarāgaṃ vā cittaṃ sarāgaṃ cittanti pajāneyyaṃ, vītarāgaṃ vā cittaṃ vītarāgaṃ "
"cittanti pajāneyyaṃ, sadosaṃ vā cittaṃ sadosaṃ cittanti pajāneyyaṃ, "
"vītadosaṃ vā cittaṃ vītadosaṃ cittanti pajāneyyaṃ, samohaṃ vā cittaṃ samohaṃ "
"cittanti pajāneyyaṃ, vītamohaṃ vā cittaṃ vītamohaṃ cittanti pajāneyyaṃ, "
"saṅkhittaṃ vā cittaṃ saṅkhittaṃ cittanti pajāneyyaṃ, vikkhittaṃ vā cittaṃ "
"vikkhittaṃ cittanti pajāneyyaṃ, mahaggataṃ vā cittaṃ mahaggataṃ cittanti "
"pajāneyyaṃ, amahaggataṃ vā cittaṃ amahaggataṃ cittanti pajāneyyaṃ, sauttaraṃ "
"vā cittaṃ sauttaraṃ cittanti pajāneyyaṃ, anuttaraṃ vā cittaṃ anuttaraṃ "
"cittanti pajāneyyaṃ, samāhitaṃ vā cittaṃ samāhitaṃ cittanti pajāneyyaṃ, "
"asamāhitaṃ vā cittaṃ asamāhitaṃ cittanti pajāneyyaṃ, vimuttaṃ vā cittaṃ "
"vimuttaṃ cittanti pajāneyyaṃ, avimuttaṃ vā cittaṃ avimuttaṃ cittanti "
"pajāneyyan’ti, "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an5.23:5.3"
msgid "tatra tatreva sakkhibhabbataṃ pāpuṇāti sati sati āyatane."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc6"></a>
#. VAR: seyyathidaṃ → seyyathīdaṃ (bj, s1-3, km, pts1)
msgctxt "an5.23:6.1"
msgid ""
"So sace ākaṅkhati: ‘anekavihitaṃ pubbenivāsaṃ anussareyyaṃ, seyyathidaṃ—"
"ekampi jātiṃ dvepi jātiyo tissopi jātiyo catassopi jātiyo pañcapi jātiyo "
"dasapi jātiyo vīsampi jātiyo tiṃsampi jātiyo cattārīsampi jātiyo paññāsampi "
"jātiyo jātisatampi jātisahassampi jātisatasahassampi anekepi saṃvaṭṭakappe "
"anekepi vivaṭṭakappe anekepi saṃvaṭṭavivaṭṭakappe—amutrāsiṃ evaṃnāmo "
"evaṃgotto evaṃvaṇṇo evamāhāro evaṃsukhadukkhappaṭisaṃvedī evamāyupariyanto, "
"so tato cuto amutra udapādiṃ; tatrāpāsiṃ evaṃnāmo evaṃgotto evaṃvaṇṇo "
"evamāhāro evaṃsukhadukkhappaṭisaṃvedī evamāyupariyanto, so tato cuto "
"idhūpapannoti, iti sākāraṃ sauddesaṃ anekavihitaṃ pubbenivāsaṃ anussareyyan’"
"ti, "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an5.23:6.2"
msgid "tatra tatreva sakkhibhabbataṃ pāpuṇāti sati sati āyatane."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli3.19"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc7"></a>
msgctxt "an5.23:7.1"
msgid ""
"So sace ākaṅkhati: ‘dibbena cakkhunā visuddhena atikkantamānusakena satte "
"passeyyaṃ cavamāne upapajjamāne hīne paṇīte suvaṇṇe dubbaṇṇe, sugate duggate "
"yathākammūpage satte pajāneyyaṃ—ime vata bhonto sattā kāyaduccaritena "
"samannāgatā vacīduccaritena samannāgatā manoduccaritena samannāgatā ariyānaṃ "
"upavādakā micchādiṭṭhikā micchādiṭṭhikammasamādānā, te kāyassa bhedā paraṃ "
"maraṇā apāyaṃ duggatiṃ vinipātaṃ nirayaṃ upapannā; ime vā pana bhonto sattā "
"kāyasucaritena samannāgatā vacīsucaritena samannāgatā manosucaritena "
"samannāgatā ariyānaṃ anupavādakā sammādiṭṭhikā sammādiṭṭhikammasamādānā, te "
"kāyassa bhedā paraṃ maraṇā sugatiṃ saggaṃ lokaṃ upapannāti, iti dibbena "
"cakkhunā visuddhena atikkantamānusakena satte passeyyaṃ cavamāne "
"upapajjamāne hīne paṇīte suvaṇṇe dubbaṇṇe, sugate duggate yathākammūpage "
"satte pajāneyyan’ti, "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an5.23:7.2"
msgid "tatra tatreva sakkhibhabbataṃ pāpuṇāti sati sati āyatane."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc8"></a>
msgctxt "an5.23:8.1"
msgid ""
"So sace ākaṅkhati: ‘āsavānaṃ khayā anāsavaṃ cetovimuttiṃ paññāvimuttiṃ "
"diṭṭheva dhamme sayaṃ abhiññā sacchikatvā upasampajja vihareyyan’ti, "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an5.23:8.2"
msgid "tatra tatreva sakkhibhabbataṃ pāpuṇāti sati sati āyatane”ti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an5.23:8.3"
msgid "Tatiyaṃ."
msgstr ""
